{{Infobox person |image = |caption = |birth_date = 15 April 1967 |birth_place = [[Lima]], [[Perú]] |birth_name = Maria Denisse Dibós Silva |Nationality = Peruvian |occupation = Actress, theatrical producer, music director, art educator, dance instructor, singer, and businessperson |years_active = |spouse = |partner = Gabriel Ortiz de Zevallos |children = 1 |parents = |relatives = }} '''María Denisse Dibós Silva''' (born 15 April 1967, [[Lima]], [[Perú]]) is a Peruvian [[actress]], [[theatrical producer]], [[music director]], [[art educator]], dance instructor, singer, and businessperson. She is creator and director of "Preludio Asociación Cultural",<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.caretas.com.pe/Main.asp?T=3082&idE=668&idS=74|title=Denisse Dibós: Ella Baila Sola|publisher=[[Caretas]]|language=Spanish|date=2006-04-20}}</ref><ref>[http://www.capital.com.pe/2013-04-25-denisse-dibos-nos-presenta-la-gran-obra-de-broadway--el-chico-de-oz-noticia_588941.html Denisse Dibós nos presenta la gran obra de Broadway: ´El Chico de Oz´]</ref> with which she has produced several musicals and plays since 1997. This musicals are adaptations of Broadway originals productions with respective rights and permissions.<ref>[http://elcomercio.pe/espectaculos/273402/noticia-denisse-dibos-abriracabaret-capital Denisse Dibós abrirá "Cabaret" en la capital]</ref><ref>[http://elcomercio.pe/espectaculos/1616941/noticia-miserables-lima-denisse-dibos-dice-que-sumaximo-sueno ¿"Los Miserables" en Lima? Denisse Dibós dice que es su "máximo sueño"]</ref>
Denise trained as a concert pianist (master in classical music) in [[California]], USA for 8 years.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.caretas.com.pe/Main.asp?T=3082&S=&id=12&idE=811&idSTo=74&idA=37166|title=Denisse Dibós: Música Maestra|publisher=Caretas|language=Spanish|date=2009-01-22}}</ref>
Dibós also worked as a teacher of the Faculty of Communication Arts and the [[Pontificia Universidad Católica del Perú]] and in Teatro de la Universidad Católica (TUC).
The musical ''[[The Boy from Oz]]'' was released in May 2013, starring [[Marco Zunino]] as Allen and produced by "Preludio A.C.".<ref>[http://m.elcomercio.pe/espectaculos/1348968/noticia-musical-broadwaythe-boy-from-oz-adaptado-lima Musical de Broadway "The Boy From Oz" será adaptado en Lima]</ref> It was the first Spanish language adaptation of this musical.<ref>[http://entretenimiento.terra.com.pe/marco-zunino-recibe-consejos-de-actor-hugh-jackman,423ce2a7be705310VgnVCM3000009af154d0RCRD.html Marco Zunino recibe consejos de actor Hugh Jackman]</ref>
== Personal life == In March 2011, she gave birth to her first daughter named Paloma, from her relationship with economist Gabriel Ortiz de Zevallos.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://elcomercio.pe/espectaculos/711148/noticia-denisse-dibos-sobre-embarazo-40-fin-conoci-persona-ideal|title=Denisse Dibós sobre embarazo a los 40: "Mi bebe tendrá el padre ideal"|publisher=''El Comercio Perú''|date=09-02-11|accessdate=10-05-12}}</ref>
